ficantly better than the hand-crafted features-based model. The\nperformance gap is reduced with bigger datasets, but considering the increased\ncomputational load, end-to-end training may not be profitable for this\napplication.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 5 Oct 2022 20:18:30 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 12 Oct 2022 18:07:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-14"}
