ective mass along the armchair direction allows for freezing out\nthe transverse degree of freedom in the electron motion.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 6 Oct 2022 06:41:10 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 24 Oct 2022 07:38:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-30"}
